{"title_page": "List of animal sanctuaries", "text_new": "{{Multiple issues|\n{{cleanup|reason=remove redlinks per [[WP:WTAF]]|date=May 2016}}\n{{external links|date=May 2016}}\n}}\n\nThis is a list of notable '''[[Animal sanctuary|animal sanctuaries]]''' from around the world.\n{{Expand list|date=August 2010}}\n{{TOC right|limit=3}}\n\n== Argentina ==\n* [[Santuario Equidad]], San Marcos Sierras, [[C\u00f3rdoba Province, Argentina|C\u00f3rdoba Province]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.facebook.com/SantuarioEquidad|title=Santuario Equidad|website=facebook.com|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elcorreogallego.es/galicia/ecg/libera-y-la-fundacion-franz-weber-proponen-crear-en-galicia-un-santuario-para-caballos-maltratados/idEdicion-2013-05-18/idNoticia-807182/|title=Libera! y la Fundaci\u00f3n Franz Weber proponen crear en Galicia un santuario para caballos maltratados|first=Grupo El Correo|last=Gallego|website=elcorreogallego.es|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n*Santuario de primates Centro Argentino de Rescate Rehabilitacion y Conservacion de primates, La Cumbre Cordoba<ref>[https://www.lanacion.com.ar/1719349-monos-caraya-el-santuario-cordobes-donde-viven-160-primates Monos caray\u00e1: el santuario cordob\u00e9s donde viven 160 primates] ''lanacion.com.ar'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n\n==Australia==\n*[[Big Ears Animal Sanctuary]], [[Longford, Tasmania]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bigearsanimalsanctuary.com/|title=Big Ears Animal Sanctuary|website=bigearsanimalsanctuary.com|accessdate=27 April 2018}}</ref>\n*[[Brightside Animal Sanctuary]], [[Cradoc, Tasmania]]<ref>[http://brightside.org.au/ \"Brightside is a registered Charity. We are a not-for-profit Farm Sanctuary and Shelter for animals set on 50 acres in Tasmania's Huon Valley\" at brightside.org.au] Accessed 6 June 2017</ref>\n*[[Edgar's Mission]], [[Lancefield, Victoria]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.edgarsmission.org.au/|title=Edgar's Mission Farm Sanctuary|website=edgarsmission.org.au|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Farm Animal Rescue]], [[Brisbane]], [[Queensland]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.farmanimalrescue.org.au|title=Farm Animal Rescue - Saving animals from a life of cruelty|website=farmanimalrescue.org.au|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Freedom Hill Sanctuary]], [[Adelaide Hills]], [[South Australia]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.freedomhill.com.au|title=Freedom Hill Sanctuary|website=freedomhill.com.au|accessdate=24 December 2019}}</ref>\n*[[Happy Hooves Farm Sanctuary]], [[Perth]], [[Western Australia]]<ref>[http://www.animalactionist.com Happy Hooves Farm Sanctuary at animalactionist.com] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n*[[Warrawong Sanctuary]], [[Adelaide]]\n\n==Bolivia==\n*[[Comunidad Inti Wara Yassi#Parque Ambue Ari|Parque Ambue Ari]], [[Santa Cruz Department (Bolivia)|Santa Cruz Department]] Run with help from volunteers by Comunidad Inti Wara Yassi.\n*[[Comunidad Inti Wara Yassi#Parque Jacj Cuisi|Parque Jacj Cuisi]], [[La Paz Department, Bolivia|La Paz Department]] Run with help from volunteers by Comunidad Inti Wara Yassi.\n*[[Comunidad Inti Wara Yassi#Parque Mach\u00eda|Parque Mach\u00eda]], [[Villa Tunari]]  Run with help from volunteers by [[Comunidad Inti Wara Yassi]].\n\n==Brazil==\n*Santu\u00e1rio das Fadas, [[Rio de Janeiro]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.vista-se.com.br/rj-nascimento-de-animais-em-seguranca-no-santuario-das-fadas/|title=RJ: Nascimento de animais em seguran\u00e7a no Santu\u00e1rio das Fadas|work=Vista-se|language=pt|date=8 October 2012|access-date=1 December 2018}}</ref>\n*Santu\u00e1rio de Elefantes Brasil, [[Chapada dos Guimar\u00e3es]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www1.folha.uol.com.br/cotidiano/2017/11/1932313-santuario-da-nova-vida-a-elefantes-mas-sofre-com-falta-de-verba-em-mt.shtml|title=Santu\u00e1rio d\u00e1 nova vida a elefantes, mas sofre com falta de verba em MT|website=Folha de S.Paulo|language=pt|date=2 November 2017|accessdate=2 November 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Canada==\n===British Columbia (BC)===\n*[[A Home for Hooves Animal Sanctuary]], [[Duncan, British Columbia|Duncan BC]]<ref>[http://www.ahomeforhoovesfarmsanctuary.com/ A Home for Hooves Farm Sanctuary Providing a Forever Home for Rescued and Abandoned Farm Animals] ''ahomeforhoovesfarmsanctuary.com'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n*[[Freedom Forest Animal Sanctuary]], [[Victoria, British Columbia|Victoria]]{{citation needed|date=November 2018}}\n*[[George C. Reifel Migratory Bird Sanctuary|George C. Reifel Migratory Bird Sanctuary, Delta]]\n*[[Hearts On Noses]], [[Mission, British Columbia|Mission]]<ref>[http://heartsonnoses.com/ Hearts On Noses - A Mini Pig Sanctuary] Accessed 29 December 2017</ref>\n*[[RASTA Animal Sanctuary, Chemainus]]<ref>[https://www.chemainusvalleycourier.ca/opinion/saving-animals-cernys-mission-at-chemainus-property/ \"Saving animals Cerny\u2019s mission at Chemainus property- RASTA Sanctuary worthy of continued support, with the third annual fundraiser coming up Nov. 4\"] Accessed 3 November 2017</ref>\n\n===Nova Scotia===\n*[[North Mountain Animal Sanctuary]], [[Burlington, Nova Scotia|Burlington]] The first sanctuary in Atlantic Canada for abused, neglected, and unwanted farm animals.\n\n===Ontario===\n\n* Animal Welfare League of Alexandria<ref>[https://alexandriaanimals.org/ Animal Welfare League of Alexandria] ''alexandriaanimals.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Aspen Valley Wildlife Sanctuary, [[Rosseau, Ontario|Rosseau]]<ref>[http://www.aspenvalley.ca/ Welcome to Aspen Valley Wildlife Sanctuary] ''aspenvalley.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Bear With Us Sanctuary and Rehabilitation Centre for Bears, [[Sprucedale, Ontario]]<ref>[http://bearwithus.org/ Bear With Us Sanctuary & Rehabilitation Centre for Bears] ''bearwithus.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Bergeron's Exotic Animal Sanctuary, [[Picton, Ontario|Picton]]<ref>[http://www.bergerons.ca Bergeron's Exotic Animal Sanctuary The Sanctuary With A Heart] ''bergerons.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Bear Creek Sanctuary, [[Barrie, Ontario]]<ref>[http://www.bearcreeksanctuary.com/main.htm Bear Creek Sanctuary at bearcreeksanctuary.com] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n* Big Sky Ranch Animal Sanctuary, [[Kemptville, Ontario|Kemptville]]<ref>[https://www.bigskyranch.ca/ Welcome to Big Sky Ranch Animal Sanctuary] ''bigskyranch.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Cedar Row Farm Sanctuary, Stratford, near [[St. Mary's, Ontario|St. Mary's]]<ref>[https://cedarrow.org/ Welcome- Cedar Row Farm Sanctuary] ''cedarrow.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Constance Creek Wildlife Refuge, [[Ottawa]] Serves as a home for over 70 farmed and domestic animals as well.<ref>[http://ccwr.ca/wildlifeinfo.html Constance Creek Wildlife Refuge- Wildlife Information] ''ccwr.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Penny Lane Farm Sanctuary, Ottawa<ref>[http://www.pennylanesanctuary.com Penny Lane Farm Sanctuary at pennylanesanctuary.com] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n* Piebird Vegan Farmstay/Sanctuary, [[Nipissing, Ontario]] Canada<ref>[http://piebird.org/ Piebird Vegan Farmstay / Farm Sanctuary] ''piebird.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* [[Rideau Valley Wildlife Sanctuary]], [[North Gower Township, Ontario|North Gower]]<ref>[https://www.canadiangeographic.ca/article/photo-gallery-rideau-valley-wildlife-sanctuary \"Photo gallery: Rideau Valley Wildlife Sanctuary\" at canadiangeographic.ca] Accessed 3 November 2017</ref>\n* RR Refuge, [[Alexandria, Ontario|Alexandria]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://refugerr.org/|title=RefugeRR - Horse Refuge for rescued horses|website=refugerr.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n* Story Book Farm Primate Sanctuary, [[Sunderland, Ontario|Sunderland]]<ref>[http://www.storybookmonkeys.org/ Story Book Farm is a place of safety] ''storybookmonkeys.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Teja's Animal Refuge, near [[Alexandria, Ontario|Alexandria]]<ref>[http://veganannie.com/2014/07/tejas-animal-refuge-a-guest-post/ Teja\u2019s Animal Refuge-a guest post] ''veganannie.com'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref> \n* [[The Donkey Sanctuary of Canada]], [[Guelph, Ontario|Guelph]]<ref>[https://www.thedonkeysanctuary.ca/ The Donkey Sanctuary of Canada] ''thedonkeysanctuary.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Wishing Well Sanctuary, [[Bradford, Ontario|Bradford]]<ref>[http://www.wishingwellsanctuary.org/ Wishing Well Sanctuary] ''wishingwellsanctuary.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Wild Bird Care Centre, [[Nepean, Ontario|Nepean]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wildbirdcarecentre.org|title=Wild Bird Care Centre|website=wildbirdcarecentre.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n===Saskatchewan===\n*Forever MicroRanch Sanctuary, near [[Frontier, Saskatchewan]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.prairiepost.com/news/2012-01-11-22-09-10/item/9382-frontier-s-farm-animal-sanctuary-owners-want-to-promote-a-more-kind-world-for-all-beings.html|title=Frontier&#039;s farm-animal sanctuary owners want to promote a more kind world for all beings - Prairie Post|last=Liebenberg|first=Matthew|access-date=2016-06-26}}</ref>\n\n===Qu\u00e9bec===\n*[[Fauna Foundation]], a chimpanzee sanctuary, [[Chambly, Qu\u00e9bec|Chambly]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.faunafoundation.org/|title=Fauna Foundation - Canada's Only Chimpanzee Sanctuary|website=faunafoundation.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Chile==\n*[[Santuario Igualdad Interespecie]], [[Santiago de Chile]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.santuarioigualdadinterespecie.org|title=Santuario Igualdad Interespecie|website=santuarioigualdadinterespecie.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Colombia==\n* Juliana's Animal Sanctuary, (note: located in Colombia, also registered for charitable purposes in [[Rockville, Maryland]])<ref>[https://julianasanimalsanctuary.org/contact-us/ Contact Us PLEASE NOTE Our Sanctuary is located in Colombia, South America, although our 501c3 charity is registered in the USA] ''julianasanimalsanctuary.org'' accessed 17 December 2018</ref>\n\n== Costa Rica ==\n* Alturas Wildlife Sanctuary, [[Dominical, Puntarenas]]<ref>[https://alturaswildlifesanctuary.org/ \"About Alturas Wildlife Sanctuary\" at alturaswildlifesanctuary.org] Accessed 6 June 2017</ref>\n* NATUWA, Macaw Sanctuary, [[Puntarenas (canton)]]<ref>[https://natuwa.com/ \"About NATUWA Macaw Sanctuary\" at natuwa.com] Accessed 13 december 2018</ref>\n\n==Cyprus==\n* See [[List of non-governmental organisations in Cyprus#Animal welfare organisations|A list of animal sanctuaries among the NGO's of Cyprus]]\n\n==Denmark==\n* Fields of Freedom Animal sanctuary, Aarup<ref>[http://fieldsoffreedom.org/ Fields of Freedom] Accessed 29 December 2017</ref>\n\n==France==\n* ADADA (\u00e2nes)<ref>[http://www.assoadada.fr/ \"ADADA (\u00e2nes)\"], via ''[https://www.l214.com/faq/quels-sont-les-refuges-pour-les-animaux-de-ferme-en-france \"L214\"]'', Accessed 20 January 2020</ref>\n* ALTERVITA<ref>[https://altervita.fr/ \"ALTERVITA\"], via ''[https://www.l214.com/faq/quels-sont-les-refuges-pour-les-animaux-de-ferme-en-france \"L214\"]'', Accessed 20 January 2020</ref>\n* AVA (animaux \u00e2g\u00e9s)<ref>[http://avarefuge.fr/ \"AVA (animaux \u00e2g\u00e9s)\"], via ''[https://www.l214.com/faq/quels-sont-les-refuges-pour-les-animaux-de-ferme-en-france \"L214\"]'', Accessed 20 January 2020</ref>\n* CHEM (chevaux)<ref>[http://www.chem.fr/ \"CHEM (chevaux)\"], via ''[https://www.l214.com/faq/quels-sont-les-refuges-pour-les-animaux-de-ferme-en-france \"L214\"]'', Accessed 20 January 2020</ref>\n* C.H.E.V.A.L. (chevaux)<ref>[https://www.refuge-cheval.com/ \"C.H.E.V.A.L. (chevaux)\"], via ''[https://www.l214.com/faq/quels-sont-les-refuges-pour-les-animaux-de-ferme-en-france \"L214\"]'', Accessed 20 January 2020</ref>\n* Des maux des mains<ref>[https://www.facebook.com/Desmauxdesmains/ \"Des maux des mains\"], via ''[https://www.l214.com/faq/quels-sont-les-refuges-pour-les-animaux-de-ferme-en-france \"L214\"]'', Access