y Ranch Animal Sanctuary, [[Kemptville, Ontario|Kemptville]]<ref>[https://www.bigskyranch.ca/ Welcome to Big Sky Ranch Animal Sanctuary] ''bigskyranch.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Cedar Row Farm Sanctuary, Stratford, near [[St. Mary's, Ontario|St. Mary's]]<ref>[https://cedarrow.org/ Welcome- Cedar Row Farm Sanctuary] ''cedarrow.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Constance Creek Wildlife Refuge, [[Ottawa]] Serves as a home for over 70 farmed and domestic animals as well.<ref>[http://ccwr.ca/wildlifeinfo.html Constance Creek Wildlife Refuge- Wildlife Information] ''ccwr.ca'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Penny Lane Farm Sanctuary, Ottawa<ref>[http://www.pennylanesanctuary.com Penny Lane Farm Sanctuary at pennylanesanctuary.com] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n* Piebird Vegan Farmstay/Sanctuary, [[Nipissing, Ontario]] Canada<ref>[http://piebird.org/ Piebird Vegan Farmstay / Farm Sanctuary] ''piebird.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* [[Rideau Valley Wildlife Sanctuary]], [[North Gower Township, Ontario|North Gower]]<ref>[https://www.canadiangeographic.ca/article/photo-gallery-rideau-valley-wildlife-sanctuary \"Photo gallery: Rideau Valley Wildlife Sanctuary\" at canadiangeographic.ca] Accessed 3 November 2017</ref>\n* RR Refuge, [[Alexandria, Ontario|Alexandria]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://refugerr.org/|title=RefugeRR - Horse Refuge for rescued horses|website=refugerr.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n* Story Book Farm Primate Sanctuary, [[Sunderland, Ontario|Sunderland]]<ref>[http://www.storybookmonkeys.org/ Story Book Farm is a place of safety] ''storybookmonkeys.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Teja's Animal Refuge, near [[Alexandria, Ontario|Alexandria]]<ref>[http://veganannie.com/2014/07/tejas-animal-refuge-a-guest-post/ Teja\u2019s Animal Refuge-a guest post] ''veganannie.com'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref> \n* [[The Donkey Sanctuary of Canada]], [[Guelph, Ontario|Guelph]]<ref>[https://www.thedonkeysanctuary.ca/ The 