unft] ''hof-narr.ch'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n* Tante Martha Animal sanctuary, [[Romont]] BE.<ref>[http://www.tante-martha.ch/ Tante Martha] ''tante-martha.ch'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n''See: [[List of reserves for waterbirds and migratory birds in Switzerland]]''\n\n==Tanzania==\n* [[Serengeti National Park]]\n\n==Thailand==\n* [[Elephant Nature Park]], [[Chiang Mai Province]]\n* Wildlife Friends Foundation Thailand, [[Phetchaburi Province]]<ref>[https://www.wfft.org/ Wildlife Friends Foundation Thailand (WFFT)] ''wfft.org'', accessed 18 November 2018</ref>\n\n==United Arab Emirates==\n* [[Sir Bani Yas]]\n* [[Ras Al Khor]]\n\n==Uganda==\n* [[Ziwa Rhino Sanctuary]] - Located approximately {{convert|176|km|mi}}, by road, north of Kampala, on the [[Kampala]]-[[Gulu]] Highway\n\n==United Kingdom==\n\n===England===\n* Bleakholt Animal Sanctuary, the Irwell Valley, near [[Edenfield]], [[Lancashire]]<ref>[http://www.bleakholt.org/ Bleakholt Animal Sanctuary] Accessed 11 September 2017</ref> \n* Bransby Horses, Bransby, [[Lincolnshire]]<ref>[https://bransbyhorses.co.uk/ Bransby Horses] Accessed 11 September 2017</ref>\n* [[Buttercups Sanctuary for Goats]] in [[Maidstone]], [[Kent]].\n* [[Cornish Seal Sanctuary]], [[Gweek]], [[Cornwall]]\n* Dean farm trust, [[Mitcheldean]]<ref>[http://www.deanfarmtrust.org.uk deanfarmtrust.org.uk] Accessed 17 January 2017</ref> \n* Farplace Animal Rescue, [[Weardale]], [[County Durham]]<ref>[http://www.farplace.co.uk/ Farplace Animal Rescue website at farplace.co.uk] Accessed 4 March 2017</ref>\n* [[Ferne Animal Sanctuary]], [[Somerset]], Wambrook, near [[Chard, Somerset|Chard]], originally run by [[Nina Douglas-Hamilton, Duchess of Hamilton]]\n* [[FRIEND Farmed Animal Rescue]], Tonbridge, Kent<ref>[http://www.friendanimalrescue.org.uk/ FRIEND Farmed Animal Rescue] Accessed 29 December 2017</ref>\n* [[Hillside Animal Sanctuary]], Frettenham, [[Norwich]]\n* [[Lower Moss Wood Educational Nature Reserve and Wildlife Hospita