ingstarr.org/ Morning Starr Animal Sanctuary] ''morningstarr.org'', Accessed 1 December 2018</ref>\n* Rescued Unwanted Furry Friends Foundation a.k.a. R.U.F.F.F. [[Mohave County, Arizona|Mohave County]]<ref>[https://www.hugssociety.org/directories/animal-shelters/united-states/arizona/928/rescued-unwanted-furry-friends-foundation.html R.U.F.F.F. Rescued Unwanted Furry Friends Foundation (Golden Valley)] ''hugssociety.org'', Accessed 1 December 2018</ref>\n\n===Arkansas===\n* Riddle's Elephant and Wildlife Sanctuary<ref>[http://elephantsanctuary.org Riddle's Elephant and Wildlife Sanctuary] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n* Turpentine Creek Wildlife Refuge<ref>[http://www.turpentinecreek.org Turpentine Creek Wildlife Refuge, Rescuing Exotic Cats Nationwide] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n\n===California===\n* [[Animal Place]], [[Grass Valley, California|Grass Valley]]\n* [[DRARS.org - Downer Ranch Animal Rescue and Sanctuary]], [[Dunlap, California|DUNLAP (Near Sequoia Kings Canyon National Park]]<ref>[http://www.drars.org DRARS.org - Downer Ranch Animal Rescue and Sanctuary] ''drars.org'', accessed 13 April 2020</ref>\n* [[Farm Sanctuary]], with locations in [[Acton, California|Acton]] (Animal Acres) and [[Orland, California|Orland]]\n* Forever Wild Exotic Animals, [[Phelan, California|Phelan]]<ref>[https://www.foreverwildsanctuary.org/ Forever Wild Exotic Animals] ''foreverwildsanctuary.org'', accessed 21 October 2018</ref>\n* The Fund for Animals Wildlife Center, San Diego County, Ramona<ref>[http://www.fundforanimals.org/wildlife-center/ The Fund for Animals Wildlife Center] ''fundforanimals.org/wildlife-center'', accessed 1 February 2019</ref>\n* The Gentle Barn, [[Santa Clarita, California|Santa Clarita]]<ref>[https://www.gentlebarn.org/ The Gentle Barn] ''gentlebarn.org'', accessed 21 October 2018</ref>\n* Goatlandia Farm Animal Sanctuary, [[Santa Rosa, California]]<ref>[https://www.goatlandia.org/ Goatlandia Farm Animal Sanctuary] ''goatlandia.org'', accesse