untain.com/|title=Wolf Mountain Sanctuary - California Wolf Educational Tours|website=wolfmountain.com|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n===Colorado===\n* Longhopes Donkey Shelter (also a donkey sanctuary), [[Bennett, Colorado|Bennett]]<ref>[http://longhopes.org/ Longhopes Donkey Shelter] Accessed 29 December 2017</ref>\n* [[Mission: Wolf]], [[Westcliffe, Colorado|Westcliffe]]\n* Peaceful Prairie Sanctuary, [[Deer Trail, Colorado|Deer Trail]]<ref>[http://peacefulprairie.org/ Peaceful Prairie Sanctuary], ''peacefulprairie.org'', accessed 1 December 2018</ref>\n* [[The Wild Animal Sanctuary]], [[Keenesburg, Colorado|Keenesburg]]\n* [[Wolf Sanctuary]], [[Bellvue, Colorado|Bellvue]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.wolfsanctuary.net/index.htm|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115080737/http://www.wolfsanctuary.net/index.htm|url-status=dead|title=Wolf Sanctuary|archivedate=15 November 2012|accessdate=23 August 2019}}</ref><ref>[http://wolfsanctuary.co/ W.O.L.F. Sanctuary, Bellvue, Colorado: Improving the quality of life for wolves and wolf dogs through Rescue, Sanctuary and Education] Accessed 29 December 2017</ref>\n\n===Florida===\n* CJ Acres Animal Rescue Farm,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cjacres.org/|title=CJ Acres Animal Rescue Farm|website=cjacres.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref> [[Keystone Heights, Florida|Keystone Heights]]\n* [[Peace River Refuge and Ranch|Forest Animal Rescue by Peace River Refuge & Ranch]], [[Silver Springs, Florida|Silver Springs]]\n* Jungle Friends Primate Sanctuary,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.junglefriends.org/|title=Jungle Friends Primate Sanctuary|website=junglefriends.org|accessdate=30 April 2017}}</ref> [[Gainesville, Florida|Gainesville]]<ref>[http://www.JungleFriends.org/ Jungle Friends Primate Sanctuary] Accessed 10 January 2017</ref>\n* Sanctuary Animal Refuge,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sanctuaryanimalrefuge.org/ |title=Sanctuary Animal Refuge |date=24 September 2004 |accessdate=30 April 2017 |url-status=bot: unkno