ce-the-debut/|title=Like a fairy tale, Yang Joon-il met his fans for the first time in 28 years since the debut {{!}} HaB Korea.net|date=2020-01-01|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-30}}</ref>\n\n== Other Ventures ==\n\n=== Endorsements ===\nIn 2019, Yang shot a commercial with Lotte Home Shopping<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/article.aspx?aid=3072077|title=Fans welcome back Yang Joon-il|website=Korea JoongAng Daily|access-date=2020-03-28}}</ref> for the first time in his life. \n\nIn 2020, Yang came in 3rd place in brand reputation rankings for male advertisement models revealed by The Korean Business Research Institute.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1380445wpp/january-male-advertisement-model-brand-reputation-rankings-revealed-2|title=January Male Advertisement Model Brand Reputation Rankings Revealed|date=2020-01-31|website=Soompi|language=en|access-date=2020-03-28}}</ref> Yang became an official model for [[Pizza Hut]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pizzahut.co.kr/|title=\ud53c\uc790\ud5db|website=PizzaHut|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-28}}</ref> He was selected as an endorsment model for [http://www.siwonschool.com/ Siwon School].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.etoday.co.kr/news/view/1858802|title=\uc288\uac00\ub9e8 \uac00\uc218 \uc591\uc900\uc77c, \uc2dc\uc6d0\uc2a4\ucfe8 \ube0c\ub79c\ub4dc \uad11\uace0 \ubaa8\ub378\ub418\ub2e4|date=2020-02-19|website=\uc774\ud22c\ub370\uc774|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-28}}</ref> He has been working as an embassador for [http://www.sikorea.co.kr/company/companyInfo Shinsegae International].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/hot-issues/view/2020/02/197476/|title=\uc591\uc900\uc77c, \uc2e0\uc138\uacc4\uc778\ud130\ub0b4\uc154\ub0a0 \uc804\uc18d\ubaa8\ub378 \ubc1c\ud0c1[\uacf5\uc2dd]|website=\uc2a4\ud0c0\ud22c\ub370\uc774|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-29}}</ref>  It was also reported that Shinsegae International is planning to launch a collaborative product with Yang.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://news.joins.com/article/23715660|title=\uc591\uc900\uc77c, \uc2e0\uc138\uacc4\uc778\ud130\ub0b4\uc154\ub0a0 \uc804\uc18d \ubaa8\ub378 \ubc1c\ud0c1 \"\uc544\ub974\ub9c8\ub2c8 \uc778\uc5f0\"|last=\uc785\ub825 2020.02.26 09:54|date=2020-02-26|website=\uc911\uc559\uc77c\ubcf4|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-29}}</ref> He appeared in commercials for [[Berocca]] by [https://www.bayer.co.kr/news/local-news-20200225/ Bayer Korea]. <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xportsnews.com/?ac=article_view&entry_id=1244725|title=\uc591\uc900\uc77c, \ubca0\ub85c\uce74 \ube44\ud0c0\ubbfc CF \uc601\uc0c1 \uacf5\uac1c\u2026&quot;\ubb34\uc2dc\ud558\ub294 \uc0ac\ub78c\uc5d0\uac8c \ub450 \ubc30\ub85c \ubcf4\uc5ec\uc918&quot;|date=2020-03-09|website=www.xportsnews.com|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-29}}</ref> He was appointed as a new face of [https://en.jennyhouse.com/ Jenny House Cosmetics].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.stardailynews.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=265637|title=\uc591\uc900\uc77c, \uc81c\ub2c8\ud558\uc6b0\uc2a4 \ucf54\uc2a4\uba54\ud2f1 \uc804\uc18d\ubaa8\ub378 \ubc1c\ud0c1... \ud2b9\ubcc4 \uc778\uc5f0 \uc787\ub294\ub2e4 ::|website=www.stardailynews.co.kr|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-29}}</ref> Jenny House Cosmetics announced to release a new product in collaboration with Yang.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://digitalchosun.dizzo.com/site/data/html_dir/2020/03/05/2020030580217.html|title=\uc81c\ub2c8\ud558\uc6b0\uc2a4, \uc591\uc900\uc77c\uacfc \ucf5c\ub77c\ubcf4\ub808\uc774\uc158\ud55c \ub9ac\ud398\uc5b4 \uc0f4\ud478 \u2018Re:BAK(\ub9ac\ubca1)\u2019 \ucd9c\uc2dc \uc608\uc815|last=Inc|first=Digital Chosun|website=digitalchosun.dizzo.com|language=ko|access-date=2020-03-29}}</ref> Re;BAK Style Repair Shampoo and Treatment was officialy launched in March and [https://www.jennyhouse.com/rebeccasalon Rebecca Salon], their collaboration site, was opened on the same day.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://biz.heraldcorp.com/view.php?ud=20200323000266|ti